Data center:

Availability zones:
Cluster of Data center

Region:
Cluster of Availability zones

Factors to consider:


Local Zones:
Low latency. Local data processing. Consistent AWS experience.

Edge locations:
Cache content in the Edge locations near the customers. Faster content delivery. Better user experience.
Does not allow to deploy apps. 
Key service is CloudFront.


